---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "3D Chalk Art Blog"
description: "Notes on 3D chalk art and mural art from artist Chris Carlson: how anamorphic illusions are made, what they cost, and how to hire a 3D chalk artist or 3D mural artist for your event or brand."
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Blog</p>
      <h1 class="display">Notes from the pavement</h1>
      <p class="lead">How 3D chalk art and murals come together, what goes into a commission, and what to know before you hire an artist.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="post-list reveal">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <article class="post-card">
        <span class="post-date"><time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time></span>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">
          <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        </a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
